Batch Watermark Photos & Logo lets you protect your photos by adding watermarks in bulk or single photo mode.
It is able to process up to 100 photos in batch, supporting all the sizes (both portrait and landscape), without any quality loss and it also provides a watermark/logo creator, an editor that lets you make your own logo!

Main Features:
- Watermark Photos in batch (up to 100 in a single shot) or in single photo mode;
- No quality loss! Supports high resolution and does not degrade the quality of the photos;
- Place the watermark wherever you want by moving it and resizing it;
- Easy to use, you add your watermark, place it and the app will process everything in few seconds!
- Watermark/Logo creator: provides a watermark editor where you can create your own logo by adding signatures, text, photos, shapes and more!
- It saves the results directly to your camera roll!

